title: Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park: Fees & Passes
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Fees & Passes              Fees & Passes           National Park Service Annual Pass NPS   Fees: There are no fees involved with visiting the Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park or the Abraham Lincoln Boyhood Home at Knob Creek. Passes: To view information concerning National Park Passes click on the Annual Pass image to the right.
